How youll help us Keep Climbing (overview & key responsibilities):
 
Lead the capture of customer data at divisional level. Responsible for creation and prioritization of new customer data features and products that provide personalized customer experiences. Responsible for creation and validation of new data sources, including data integrity across our data structures. Also responsible for using advanced analytics and machine learning to develop actionable insights that drive improvement in customer satisfaction, revenue generation and operational efficiency.
 
Responsible for end to end product ownership for customer data including: understanding the business problem, identifying user needs, and developing optimal solution
 Partner with IT, Customer Experience Strategy, Operations and Commercial Business Units to develop customer data product enhancements that fit business needs and provide value
 Design, model and create data sources and systems that will support Reservations, Customer Care and Digital Engagement strategies
 Develop advanced analytics solutions for complex business problems
 Develop and implement reporting tools and performance management systems that generate actionable insights, drive accountability, and improve Reservations performance
 Advance business understanding and implementation of artificial intelligence technologies as well as data science best practices
 Performs analysis for benchmarking, business case development, and strategy recommendations for Reservations teams
 Mentor business analysts in technical proficiency and business acumen
 Role models core values in alignment with Deltas Rules of the Road
